snippet.title: MonsterSoft Trailer
snippet.description:
Manage a game-dev company where your only employees are skillful monsters in this turn-based game. Destroy humans in your free time.

Find more information on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1396480/MonsterSoft/
